<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361548" n="1"/>
<opener>
   <lb/>Viro <abbr>Celeber.</abbr> et <abbr>Illustriss.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs>
   <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517">Petrus <abbr>Ant.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> Michelotti</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
</opener>
<p>
   <lb/>Mihi gaudeo quod <abbr>Illustr.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus Tuus</rs> benignissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>me Tibi significari jusserit se meam <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Disserta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionem</rs> lecturum et correcturum. Hanc igitur
               <lb/>in ordinem redigo, et diligenter scribo; deinde
   <lb/>eam ipsam ad illum per <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3173435">Mediolanum</rs> mittam
               <lb/>absque eo quod ille quidquam solvat. Tibi gratias
               <lb/>refero maximas pro tanto beneficio uti etiam
               <lb/>pro iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> respondisti ad qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sita mea in
   <lb/>nuperis tuis humanissimis <rs type="letters" key="B_1717-12-16_991170517037405501 B_1717-12-16_991170517037405501">literis</rs><!-- ToDo: kontrollieren, ob beide ausgezeichneten Briefe gemeint sind oder nur einer. -->, post quas
               <lb/>protinus fere accepi humanissimam Marchio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nis <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11887733X">Poleni</rs> <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs><!-- brieftag. ToDo: Im vorigen Brief kontrollieren, was gemeint ist. -->. Interim te rogo ut
   <lb/>salutem plurimam mittas meo nomine
   <lb/>ad <abbr>Celeber.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruum</rs> et <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruelem</rs> Tuum,
               <lb/>et ut venias huc quamprimum in domum
   <lb/>meam opto, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>soque. Accepi nuper <abbr>Cele<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ber.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260">Scheuchzeri</rs> <rs type="letter">literas</rs><!-- brieftag ToDo: kontrollieren, ob Brief von Johannes Scheuchzer an Michelotti erhalten ist. --> cum <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_6CBDPU2E">operis Agrostogra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>phici sane utilis et pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clari Idea</rs>. Ipse revera
   <lb/>eminet inter Illustres rei botanic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Scriptores<supplied>.</supplied>
               <lb/>Utinam omnes illum cognoscere vellent.
            </p>
<closer>Vale
   <lb/>Vir Amicissime mihique favere perge.
   <lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Venetiis</rs> <date when="1719-01-05"><choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan> a dato</expan></choice> 5 Januarii <formula>\frac{1718}{1719}</formula> <choice><abbr>m. v.</abbr><expan>more veneto.</expan></choice></date></dateline>
</closer>
